data.description: Beautifully Remodeled CUSTOM Single story, HOME in the Villa Serena community - A 2.75% Assumable VA Mortgage!  Light, bright & open floor plan w 2 living areas, formal dining + office with Kiva fireplace, Custom built-in desk, cabinets, bookcases, large closet with 6 large built-in cabinets internet ready or 3rd bedroom. Lots of updated features throughout - Floors, Lights, Kitchens, Baths, ++ Living room w kiva fireplace open to dining room. Kit w breakfast nook & pantry. Main bedroom suite w luxurious bath & walk-in closet. 2nd bed w double walk-in closets. Lots of Storage! Carefree Living w Clubhouse, Pool, Sauna, privacy.  In Four Hills with Country Club & Golf course!! Monthly dues cover water, trash, sewage, landscape upkeep, exterior painting, swimming pool & clubhouse.
